  "title": "Tooling Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>To be responsible for Tooling Department for design,\nCAM, fabrication, quotation till customer approval of project.</li><li>To be responsible for achieving budget and forecast.</li><li>To meet Company’s strategic target for KPI entrusted.</li><li>To ensure and maintain high quality of work all processes for Milling, Grinding,\nCNC Milling, EDM, EDB, Wire Cut machining, diamond turning process, including\njig and fixture design for fabrication.</li><li>To spearhead and lead in enhancing process capability, efficiency, yield and\nmachine maintenance meeting OEE target, adhering to health, safety and\nenvironmental requirements.</li><li>To provide an effective process fabrication plan for Tooling towards automation.</li><li>To troubleshoot and provide solutions on technical problems on all Tooling.</li></ul>",
